1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,120
This challenge is not about strength, but about logic and coordination.

2
00:00:05,120 --> 00:00:10,560
Your goal will be to complete the color patterns shown on screen.

3
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:16,040
You will see one pattern for each terminal, made up of different color segments.

4
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:21,600
To achieve this, you will use your tokens and the terminal buttons.

5
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:28,000
Each token contains three hidden colors. To discover them, place the token on any terminal.

6
00:00:28,080 --> 00:00:31,760
And press the black, red, and green buttons.

7
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:35,440
Each button will light up one of that token's colors.

8
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:40,080
And those colors will always be the same, no matter where it is.

9
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:45,120
You will need to move between terminals, using each token where it is most useful.

10
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:49,120
That is how you will complete the missing segments in each pattern.

11
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:53,360
Discover, combine, and coordinate quickly.

12
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:57,280
If time reaches zero, the phase will reset.

13
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:59,950
Understand the system and make it yours.
